{"id": "ChIJMdtjLv-7woARY1Qx1otbqZI", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 1056, "displayName": {"text": "SUGARFISH by sushi nozawa", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Sugarfish Beverly Hill's spare, hidden private dining room offers a 20-course Japanese tasting menu.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJMdtjLv-7woARY1Qx1otbqZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xSVVqUnNSR3hmY21WRVZ6aElUa1ZRVXpaQlUzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "You can’t go wrong with Sugarfish. The sushi is always delicious, incredibly fresh, and consistently high quality. I usually order takeout, and they are always fast and right on time, it’s my go-to sushi spot. I probably order at least three times a month.\n\nThe packaging is also very thoughtfully done, with each piece separated perfectly so everything arrives just as it should. They really think about every detail, and that’s what makes them special. Highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "You can’t go wrong with Sugarfish. The sushi is always delicious, incredibly fresh, and consistently high quality. I usually order takeout, and they are always fast and right on time, it’s my go-to sushi spot. I probably order at least three times a month.\n\nThe packaging is also very thoughtfully done, with each piece separated perfectly so everything arrives just as it should. They really think about every detail, and that’s what makes them special. Highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Soraya Teffaha", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108003745736305981958/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLSmBiP7G8qW2UMTc4k4OlqRYa2hksDVlFcGPFMZTUkcOPB7qsyA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-19T06:06:39.823480695Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xSVVqUnNSR3hmY21WRVZ6aElUa1ZRVXpaQlUzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xSVVqUnNSR3hmY21WRVZ6aElUa1ZRVXpaQlUzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bbff2e63db31:0x92a95b8bd6315463"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMdtjLv-7woARY1Qx1otbqZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWcE5ITnRUWHBrTFhZMmJUaHJXWFJ1UWtRelZtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great dining experience. The Trust Me menu delivers consistently fresh fish and perfectly seasoned rice. Service is efficient and polished, making it a reliable go to when you want quality sushi without distractions. Portions are normal for sushi standards, a bit expensive but its worth it given its in beverly hills and the quality. Servers very nice and polite.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great dining experience. The Trust Me menu delivers consistently fresh fish and perfectly seasoned rice. Service is efficient and polished, making it a reliable go to when you want quality sushi without distractions. Portions are normal for sushi standards, a bit expensive but its worth it given its in beverly hills and the quality. Servers very nice and polite.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alicia Roman", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111662361686819594642/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIl2nygnflm2FyCuPk1LzVbfNlVOo34d3nnUnOaXD-88Pz8kA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-01T03:48:26.668404111Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWcE5ITnRUWHBrTFhZMmJUaHJXWFJ1UWtRelZtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWcE5ITnRUWHBrTFhZMmJUaHJXWFJ1UWtRelZtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bbff2e63db31:0x92a95b8bd6315463"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMdtjLv-7woARY1Qx1otbqZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KRmNtaGtTazl1Y1RSWGFUazRPVnAyUTNORVZWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "The green tea tastes like mug water, the were out of sashimi and it was one order per table(?)\nI came to the sushi place and they don’t have basic ingredients? They were out of tuna.\nThey don’t have warm edamame, freezing cold edamame was served and portion was it’s like they stole it from someone’s table.\nOverall bad very bad. On top when I got home I had the worst stomach ache….\nClose down or level up.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The green tea tastes like mug water, the were out of sashimi and it was one order per table(?)\nI came to the sushi place and they don’t have basic ingredients? They were out of tuna.\nThey don’t have warm edamame, freezing cold edamame was served and portion was it’s like they stole it from someone’s table.\nOverall bad very bad. On top when I got home I had the worst stomach ache….\nClose down or level up.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Medina Akhmedova", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114480248969078988139/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCWVtUIutJj9uTttaHEa4Xz161x1JPjmR81d_Sq8i0viaVBdoL=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-11T16:34:52.526784478Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KRmNtaGtTazl1Y1RSWGFUazRPVnAyUTNORVZWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KRmNtaGtTazl1Y1RSWGFUazRPVnAyUTNORVZWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bbff2e63db31:0x92a95b8bd6315463"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMdtjLv-7woARY1Qx1otbqZI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KUFZtVjFMVmhXZDJjNFpWWmpXVXhQZW5CUlQyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "We informed the waitress of severe gluten sensitivity for one of the members of our party who had celiac. She assured us no problem they could do everything gluten free. We ordered a full tasting menu as she recommended. The first course was soggy cold edamame. The second was toro sashimi which were cut in weird pieces that felt like scraps. We asked for gluten free soy sauce or tamari and they told us they didn’t have any and in the future we should bring our own. The waitress was unpleasant bordering rude. We also wanted a side of sushi rice - of which we were denied. Overall they were very unaccommodating, the atmosphere was weird. We opted to leave and just pay for what we’d received. They charged us $33 for the scraps of sashimi, at full price as opposed to the portion of the price of what we originally ordered.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We informed the waitress of severe gluten sensitivity for one of the members of our party who had celiac. She assured us no problem they could do everything gluten free. We ordered a full tasting menu as she recommended. The first course was soggy cold edamame. The second was toro sashimi which were cut in weird pieces that felt like scraps. We asked for gluten free soy sauce or tamari and they told us they didn’t have any and in the future we should bring our own. The waitress was unpleasant bordering rude. We also wanted a side of sushi rice - of which we were denied. Overall they were very unaccommodating, the atmosphere was weird. We opted to leave and just pay for what we’d received. They charged us $33 for the scraps of sashimi, at full price as opposed to the portion of the price of what we originally ordered.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alyssa Behr", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100095915388174347455/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXthvMDnDfiKBKgObPhjhoBVCVrhk5FSgvmL3B_83tDfrlwRzB0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-07T23:52:45.307602483Z", "flagContentUri": 